title: price controls
description: Nyambo pamusoro pema 'Price Controls" akaiswa ne hurumende yeZimbabwe nguva yanga yakaoma zvinhu 2000 - 2009. Hurumende ndiyo yanga yava kushara mitengo yezvinhu pa nguva iyi.

title: roora
description: Nyambo dzinoenderana nezvinoitika pama roora. Roora muripo unobviswa nomunhurume kana achinge avekuda kugara nomunhukadzi.

title: Mapurisa (ZRP)
description: "Mapurisa" is Shona word for Police. Ngonjo, Dhikazi, Porisi are some of the slang words for police.

title: system tazvida
description: System Tazvida muimbi ano nyanyo zivikanwa ne nziyo yake inonzi "Anodyiwa Haataure".

title: gumbura
description: Robert Martin Gumbura mufundisi akatongerwa 40years mutirongo paakawanikwa aine mhosva dzakati kuti dzechibharo.

title: Jah Prayzah
description: Mukudzeyi Mukombe, who performs under the name Jah Prayzah, is a Zimbabwean contemporary musician and lead member for the band Third Generation.
